+       | BG_Magenta | BG_Cyan | BG_Gray | BG_Default -> BG_Default
 
-    | BG_Black | BG_Red | BG_Green | BG_Yellow | BG_Blue 
-    | BG_Magenta | BG_Cyan | BG_Gray | BG_Default -> BG_Default
